Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.50,Main,Sign,0,0,0,,{\b1\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\c&H071113&\3c&H40AD77&\4c&H40AD77&\pos(231.385,274.615)}{Buried}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.25,Main,Prontea,0,0,0,,{I couldn't find them...}Không tìm thấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:07.78,Main,Ysley,0,0,0,,{I figured as much.}Em biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.69,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{Damn... Why didn't I account for a \Nsubterranean escape in the first place?}Chết tiệt...Sao mình không tính đến chuyện này nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.70,Italics,Ysley,0,0,0,,{We'll probably never get \Nanother chance like this.}Chắc chắn lần sau chúng sẽ cẩn thận hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:16.95,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{That was a close one!}Nguy hiểm quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:19.17,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,{But what's going on? How'd they find us?!}Nhưng sao chúng lại tìm ra chúng ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.66,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{We used an alias when we checked in.\N They must have looked into it.}Chúng ta đã sử dụng tên giả\N khi đăng kí, có vẻ chúng đã tìm ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:26.73,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{We may never be safe \Nentering a human town again.}Có vẻ không nên bước vào lãnh thổ nhân loại nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.65,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,{Oh, no!}Không chịu đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.47,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,{Does that mean we have to stay underground?}Vậy ta cứ phải ở dưới đất mãi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:37.18,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,{Without any beds or baths? No way!}Không có giường lẫn bồn tắm? Không chịu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:44.41,Italics,Kroft,0,0,0,,{Things are too dangerous to spend long \Nlistening to this moron's bullshit...}Mất thời gian thuyết phục con ngu này phiền thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.24,Italics,Kroft,0,0,0,,{But that doesn't change the fact\N that I need her power.}Nhưng mình vẫn cần sức mạnh của nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:49.57,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,Kroft...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.20,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{I don't want you to die, Raki.}Anh không muốn em chết, Raki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.73,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{I'll try to comfort you \Nthrough the painful parts...}Anh sẽ cố gắng giúp em thấy thoải mái nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.71,Main,Kroft,0,0,0,,{So please, listen to me.}Nên làm ơn nghe anh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.64,Main,Raki,0,0,0,,{O-Okay...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.96,Italics,Kroft,0,0,0,,{Damn it. I hate to do this, \Nbut there's no other way.}Thiệt tình, khó chịu quá nhưng đành phải vậy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:08.60,Italics,Kroft,0,0,0,,{I guess I'll love you.}Ta sẽ yêu ngươi.
