Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.39,Main,Bonnie,0,0,0,,{Screw you assholes!}Khốn kiếp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.27,Main,Bonnie,0,0,0,,{\an8}{You think I'm too slow with heals?}Cái gì mà chữa thương lâu chứ?
